.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, iced-tea, tea
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, brown, fuchsia, yellow
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, reading, writing, video-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who likes coral is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking cola##2
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk | tea     | iced-tea     |
| Color   | brown      | coral       | yellow | fuchsia |
| Hobby           | writing       | video-games    | reading     | collecting         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

