 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
 9. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person driving the taxi is the person drinking lemonade##1
12. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5

.:: Answer ::.
