 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is between the person traveling to nizza and the person drinking sprite##2
