 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
10. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
11. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
13. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5

.:: Answer ::.
