The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, dubstep, techno
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog, bird
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 2. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 8. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 9. the owner of the bird is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of d&b is in an even position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
12. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
