 1. the person playing chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
 4. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 7. the german is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
 9. the polish is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
13. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

