.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, taxi, quad-bike, airplane
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, punk, r&b
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan of r&b##2
 4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the fan of r&b##5
 5. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 6. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the fan of reggae##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
12. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Beverage      | water   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea   | sprite          |
| Transport          | taxi    | airplane        | quad-bike     | train          |
| Music-Genre           | reggae | punk        | dubstep | r&b |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, journalist, musician
City: venice, boston, san-francisco, paris
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, parkour, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the architect##3
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the doctor is between the journalist and the person traveling to paris##2
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
 7. the journalist is the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
10. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Job           | musician   | architect  | doctor        | journalist |
| City   | venice     | paris     | san-francisco      | boston   |
| Sport     | rugby | parkour | snowboarding          | basketball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, scooter, trike, boat
City: hamburg, miami, london, boston
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the fan of soul is the person driving the van##1
 3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the person traveling to london is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | van | trike  | boat    | scooter       |
| City           | miami  | boston | london | hamburg  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 